_sText:
Thank you for downloading gg_orrery.

This is a second collaborative project with mapper RadLionheart.

Features a dynamic environment with huge spinning orrery rings and globe. The style was based on a previous map I'd made, gg_vast, in the same manner of layout, texuring, and theory.

Perfect for short range weapons, long range weapons, knifing and hegrenades.

This map also has buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have this on any non-gungame server.

All textures created by myself.
Skybox texture created by Karatekaefer. Am I mooching from him or putting his excellent work to use? :P

If you'd like to play this map on our gg server, please join us at:

208.146.44.32:27015

or visit us on the fourms:

http://seattle-ducksoup.com/index.php

Thank you!

--Manqueef/Emeriastone & RadLionheart
